gnizing this fact allows for interesting questions to be asked regarding\nthe actions of those, such as Bellarmine, who were responding to the work of\nCopernicus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 16:35:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
