\nof the two transitions. Critical ER graphs provide a pictorial representation\nof the Hilbert space of a generic many-body Hamiltonian with short range\ninteractions. In particular we argue that their phase diagram can be mapped\nonto the out-of-equilibrium phase diagram of the quantum random energy model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 22:45:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 17:45:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2022 16:02:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
