 room temperature, the light yield\nof our acrylic sample relative to the TPB sample is 0.3 %, while it reaches 0.5\n% at 4 K. The main fluorescence time constant of the acrylic is less than a few\nnanoseconds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 23:55:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
