ons with those\nobtained using as input the central PDFs from the 3-flavour NLO PDF sets of the\nCT14, ABMP16 and NNPDF3.1 collaborations show that far-forward neutrino energy\ndistributions vary by as much as a factor of $\\sim 2-4$ relative to the PROSA19\npredictions at TeV neutrino energies. The Forward Physics Facility in the high\nluminosity LHC era will provide data capable of constraining NLO QCD\nevaluations with these PDF sets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Dec 2021 01:06:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2022 04:04:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-04"}
